        "content": "Web search results for query: \"February 2026 AI coding CLI terminal agent launch Claude Code Gemini Codex alternative\"\n\nI'll perform a web search for that query about AI coding CLI terminal agents.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"ai编程工具 Claude API 国内如何使用配置ClaudeCode\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/weiyilei2007/article/details/158382450\"},{\"title\":\"Claude、OpenAI Codex、Google Gemini 编程系列大比拼\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/a7609257915970535942/\"},{\"title\":\"一天一个开源项目（第27篇）：Awesome AI Coding - 一站式 AI 编程资源导航\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/chendongqi2007/article/details/158206174\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code 一键启动+自动安装：macOS 图形化工具，支持四种终端\",\"url\":\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000047612227\"},{\"title\":\"青蛙小白\",\"url\":\"https://blog.frognew.com/\"},{\"title\":\"阿甘兄\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_20042935\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code、Codex、OpenCode 和 Gemini CLI的介绍\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44162814/article/details/157763067\"},{\"title\":\"aicoding\",\"url\":\"http://www.github.com/topics/aicoding\"},{\"title\":\"2026最新ai编程工具，一键配置ClaudeCode、GeminiCLI与codex\",\"url\":\"https://www.bilibili.com/read/mobile/45073951\"},{\"title\":\"ai编程工具 灵芽API一键配置ClaudeCode、GeminiCLI与codex\",\"url\":\"https://developer.volcengine.com/articles/7600232945502011401\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found comprehensive information about AI coding CLI terminal agents and their launches/development around February 2026. Here's what I discovered:\n\n## **Main AI Coding CLI Tools in February 2026**\n\n### **1. Claude Code (Anthropic)**\n- **Base Model**: Claude 4.5\n- **Key Strengths**: \n  - Strongest logical refactoring capabilities\n  - Full Shell permissions (file read/write, Git, Shell access)\n  - True **agentic execution** mode\n- **Common Issues**: Strict protocol header validation (prone to 403 errors)\n\n### **2. Gemini CLI (Google)**\n- **Base Model**: Gemini 3 Pro / Gemini 3.1 Pro\n- **Key Strengths**:\n  - **1M-2M+ ultra-long context window**\n  - Engineering audit capabilities\n  - Analytical execution mode\n- **Common Issues**: Complex authentication, cross-border latency\n- **Positioning**: More like \"ChatGPT + Google Search in the terminal\" rather than a pure coding agent\n\n### **3. CodeX / Codex (OpenAI)**\n- **Base Model**: GPT-5.2-Codex / GPT-5.3-Codex (released February 5-12, 2026)\n- **Key Strengths**:\n  - High logic generation stability\n  - Extremely fast response\n  - Special coding agent design (GPT-5.3-Codex-Spark ultra-fast real-time version launched February 12)\n- **Limitation**: Relatively limited context window (128K-400K)\n- **Execution Mode**: Fill-in-middle (no terminal access, code output only)\n\n## **Key Industry Trend - February 2026**\n\nThe search results reveal a major paradigm shift occurring in February 2026:\n\n> **\"From 'Completion Plugins' to 'Autonomous Agents'**\n\nThe focus of AI-assisted development has officially shifted from **\"conversational completion within IDEs\"** to **\"CLI-based agentic execution\"**.\n\nDeveloper expectations have evolved from:\n- **Old**: Copilot-style single-line prompts\n- **New**: \"Here's the error message, please autonomously enter the terminal, fix it, and run tests to verify results\"\n\n## **Why CLI Agents Are Replacing Traditional IDE Plugins**\n\n1. **From \"Black Box Completion\" to \"Transparent Agent\"**: CLI tools like Claude Code have terminal access, can autonomously run test scripts, and fix issues based on stack traces - creating an automated \"generate-run-fix\" loop\n\n2. **Deep Cross-File Context Awareness**: Tools like Gemini CLI with million-token native context allow inputting entire project source code, dependency trees, and commit history for architect-level global vision\n\n3. **True Autonomy**: These agents can execute commands, modify files, interact with Git, and perform actual development workflows rather than just generating code snippets\n\n## **Summary Comparison for Engineering/Research Use Cases**\n\n| Use Case | Recommended Tool |\n|----------|------------------|\n| Engineering/Scientific coding | **Claude Code** (strongest CLI-level coding agent) |\n| IDE-based coding | **Codex** |\n| Agent research | **OpenCode** |\n| Quick reference/documentation | **Gemini CLI** (smarter command-line encyclopedia) |\n\nThe search results consistently show that **Claude Code** is currently regarded as the strongest CLI-level coding agent for actual engineering and research work.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
